    "updated_at": "2023-07-13T18:15:44Z",
    "body": "Because the starship (bash) initialization is incompatible with any pure POSIX-shell, I would avoid putting `eval \"$(starship init bash)\"` into `~/.profile` which may be sourced by POSIX-only shells. Please only use the bash-specific files instead, as recommended in the installation guide.",
